query:
/*+  */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 0 AND q1.view_count <= 100
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join tag AS t1
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('circles',
'compactness',
'differential-topology',
'epsilon-delta',
'matrix-equations',
'numerical-linear-algebra',
'real-numbers',
'recursion',
'self-learning',
'sobolev-spaces',
'supremum-and-infimum',
'transformation',
'updates')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND u1.downvotes >= 10 AND u1.downvotes <= 100000
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND b.name IN ('Benefactor',
'Favorite Question',
'Great Answer',
'Inquisitive',
'Reviewer',
'Self-Learner',
'Tag Editor',
'Talkative',
'Tumbleweed')
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
